page.title: 18Ecology.
page.content: The trees which are growing are deciduous hardwoods,hornbeam,ash, elder and oak.The undergrowth is mainlly stinging nettles.There is no access at all to the quarry where sand and gravel was quarried but which has now been abandoned. Our area is very isolated.There are only two cottages but the road going through the area is very busy.One car passed us every minute or so.The area is mostly woodland apart from the abandonded quarry.It is very difficult to walk along the road because there is no path.
